Policy.acknowledgement_statement: Funding support for the study “Genetic Analysis of Quantitative Facial Variation” was provided by the National Institute of Dental and Craniofacial Research (NIDCR; grant number X01-HG007821). Genotyping services and assistance with genotype QC were funded by the NIDCR, and provided by the Center for Inherited Disease Research (CIDR) and the University of Washington through a federal contract from the National Institutes of Health (NIH) to The Johns Hopkins University, contract number HHSN268200782096C. Data and samples were obtained through: (1) the Center for Craniofacial and Dental Genetics at the University of Pittsburgh, funded by grants U01-DE020078 and R01-DE016148 from the NIDCR; (2) the University of Colorado (Denver), funded by grant U01-DE020054 from the NIDCR; and (3) the University of Iowa, funded by grant U01-DE020057 from the NIDCR and grant R01-DD000295 from the Centers for Disease Control. The datasets used for the analyses described in this manuscript were obtained from dbGaP at [INSERT URL] through dbGaP accession number [INSERT ACCESSION NUMBER].
